{"tid":219811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"時間每天渡過 但有幾多會淡忘","createTime":"2017-04-27T13:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T06:47:46.000Z","uid":88518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f7b575b26afb48a3452197ebcbf7ed39b89de3","tid":219811,"uid":88518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:05:25.000Z","msg":"你係我心靈最脆弱既時候出現 無聲無息咁進入左我既世界<br />\n如果有得簡 我情願無認識過你 至少大家都唔會咁難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地既愛根本唔應該存在係呢個世界上 唔捨得又可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我每日都安慰自己人生就係會不斷充滿遺憾 希望我同你都可以走出黎 忘記對方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天起各有日後<br />\n如花火攜不走 無需要定擁有"},{"pid":"ebee21a0d517f095db961ddba1a176ed86b6fd4a","tid":219811,"uid":50969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:17:17.000Z","msg":"到依刻我都同自己講<br />\n求剝奪記憶"},{"pid":"766ed03681b42f964b0b659f31db4c112e5b1814","tid":219811,"uid":88518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到依刻我都同自己講<br />\n求剝奪記憶</blockquote><br />\n我會將呢份愛放在我內心既最深處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9821451b3e1d5cfea975100d1de1ed60eb6b83","tid":219811,"uid":98805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到依刻我都同自己講<br />\n求剝奪記憶</blockquote><br />\n我會將呢份愛放在我內心既最深處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得好<br />\n逝去感情如何留得住."}]}